
Virtus.ai is a 6 months old software development company currently having 4 software developers. The company is currently juggling multiple projetcts wile developing their core product Netpuno.
Netptuno is a cloud platform that allows retailers to search for products in a natural way.

In order to manage the workload the team uses Trello organized in a Kanban way and Git is used for version control.

Tests developed are unitary, integration and manual and they are run before each build is created.

Communication is handled directly or using slack.

From the live instances, user query's, tbe time the time the user uses the service.

Infrastructure is managed using the Azure platform and Docker.